
## The Counterfeit Killer

The Counterfeit Killer is a 1968 American crime film directed by JÃ³zef Lejtes and written by Steven Bochco and Harold Clements. The film stars Jack Lord, Shirley Knight, Jack Weston, Charles Drake, Joseph Wiseman and Don Hanmer. The film was released in May 1968, by Universal Pictures.

